sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Cliente
    participant Gateway as API Gateway
    participant Consul as Consul Server
    participant Service as Servicio Destino

    Client->>+Gateway: GET /api/haberes/etec/recurso
    
    Gateway->>+Consul: Descubrir(haberes-etec-service)
    Consul-->>-Gateway: service-url (192.168.x.x:port)

    Gateway->>+Service: GET /api/haberes/etec/recurso (routed)
    Service-->>-Gateway: 200 OK (Datos)

    Gateway-->>-Client: 200 OK (Datos)
